ABOUT US
Here at Golden Eagle Country Club we pride ourselves on the high quality of magnificent golf, superb amenities and outstanding service that we offer our valued customers. We have worked for over thirty years to become a staple of the community, and in the process we have earned recognition as one of the region’s premier golf experiences.

GOLDEN EAGLE GOLF & COUNTRY CLUB MEMBERSHIP INFORMATION
Member Log in
Full Family Golfing Membership, limited to 450. For the entire Family to enjoy all amenities of the Club.
Junior Executive Golf Membership, (Prior to 34th birthday) included in the above limit of 450. Allows for all Junior Executive members to convert to a full membership at the Golf Membership rate in effect at the time of joining, less the amount they paid at the time they joined.
Non-Resident membership, for persons residing outside 60 mile radius of Tallahassee.
Associate Membership, limit of 100. A family golfing membership, provides full golfing privileges except on weekends and holidays, prior to 1 PM. Tee times restricted to a maximum of 3 days in advance.
Single Membership, Golf and all privileges for unmarried individuals with no resident children.
Swimming, Tennis, & Dining, for the entire family, allows for unlimited golf privileges during the calendar year by paying guest green and cart fees.
Dining Membership for enjoyment of all dining facilities and social functions. Allows golfing privileges four (4) times in a calendar year paying guest green and cart fees.
Family Tennis & Dining Membership, for the entire family, allows golfing privileges four (4) times in a calendar year paying guest green and cart fees.
Single Tennis & Dining Membership, for singles, allows golfing privileges four (4) times in a calendar year paying guest green and cart fees.
